# Files NOT uploaded to Vercel deploys from this repo root.
# IMPORTANT: BOTH the `calma-api` and `calma` (web) projects deploy from the repo root and SHARE this
# file, so it must exclude ONLY universally-safe cruft — never a source dir (web/, control_plane/, api/,
# .claude/), or one project's build would lose its source. The API function bundle is trimmed separately
# via api.vercel.json `excludeFiles`.

# secrets + local env (the deployed side uses `vercel env`, never a committed/local file)
.env
.env.*
.env.example

# OS / tool caches + regenerated build outputs (Vercel rebuilds these)
**/.DS_Store
**/__pycache__/
**/*.pyc
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.next/
dist/
node_modules/
